{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rspec/rspec-core/issues/174","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rspec/rspec-core","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rspec/rspec-core/issues/174/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rspec/rspec-core/issues/174/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rspec/rspec-core/issues/174/events","html_url":"https://github.com/rspec/rspec-core/issues/174","id":349003,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWUzNDkwMDM=","number":174,"title":"Rake task rspec_opts is ignored when rcov=true","user":{"login":"cgriego","id":4805,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjQ4MDU=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/4805?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/cgriego","html_url":"https://github.com/cgriego","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cgriego/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cgriego/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cgriego/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cgriego/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cgriego/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cgriego/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cgriego/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cgriego/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cgriego/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[],"state":"closed","locked":true,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":3,"created_at":"2010-10-06T05:43:42Z","updated_at":"2010-10-06T12:47:36Z","closed_at":"2010-10-06T13:12:52Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"This worked in beta.20:\n\n```\nRSpec::Core::RakeTask.new(:rcov => 'db:test:prepare') do |t|\n    t.spec_opts = [\"--\", \"--profile\", \"--format progress\"]\n    t.rcov      = true\n    t.rcov_opts = \"--failure-threshold --rails --exclude test/*,spec/*,features/*,gems/*,forklift_client/*\"\nend\n```\n\nThis task overwrote the defaults rspec opts in the project's .rspec file. Now task.[r]spec_opts is ignored if rcov is true. The rake task should instead append these options on the end of the command. Ideally this code:\n\n```\nRSpec::Core::RakeTask.new(:rcov => 'db:test:prepare') do |t|\n    t.rspec_opts = [\"--profile\", \"--format progress\"]\n    t.rcov       = true\n    t.rcov_opts  = \"--failure-threshold\"\nend\n```\n\nWould result in the following command: `rcov -Ispec --failure-threshold files/to/run -- --profile --format progress`, noting that \"--\" does not appear in the task declaration.\n","closed_by":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rspec/rspec-core/issues/174/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rspec/rspec-core/issues/174/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}